-Restores & rejuvenates for a youthful appearance
-Restore even skin tone

-Improve discomfort and functionality
-Minimally invasive, outpatient procedure

Women should enjoy sex at every age. Real Dr. Feelgood specializes in female sexual dysfunction and optimization.

The O-Shot, commonly called the Orgasm Shot or the vagina injection is the popular new treatment hailed as the “Viagra for women.” The O-Shot is a drug-free, non-surgical solution that rejuvenates the female genitalia. 

With the orgasm shot, women experience better sex from increased libido, stronger and more frequent orgasms, greater clitoral arousal, and the ability to have vaginal orgasms. 

In addition, the orgasm shot can alleviate intimate problems that women commonly encounter, including dryness, incontinence, painful intercourse (dyspareunia) and vaginal looseness.

-Restores & rejuvenates for a youthful appearance

-Minimally invasive, outpatient procedure
